Basic fenced comment:

```
Before.

%%%
This is a comment.
%%%

After.
.
<p>Before.</p>
<p>After.</p>
```

Fenced comment with blank lines:

```
%%%
First line.

Second line.
%%%
.
```

Fenced comment with longer fence:

```
%%%%
%%% not the end
still inside
%%%%
.
```

Closing fence must match length:

```
%%%%
comment
%%%
still comment
%%%%
.
```

Unclosed fenced comment consumes rest of document:

```
%%%
This comment never closes.
.
```
